{
  "wireMagic": "pb3",
  "pens": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wsWinStyles": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wpWinPositions": [ {
  
  } ],
  "events": [ {
    "tStartMs": 0,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think AI and especially\nhow students use AI,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2460,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's very telling of those motivations."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 4650,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, there are some\nstudents who are using it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6780,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to complete work for them,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 8010,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, to do it on their behalf."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 9330,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there are some students who, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 10830,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are staying away from AI,\nor using it proactively."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13710,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They're using it in ways that\nreinforce their learning."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15900,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's our responsibility now as students"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17820,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to, you know, use this tool"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 19830,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to, you know, achieve your\nown individual outcomes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 22950,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Everyone is talking about\nhow AI is changing education,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 26100,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but we figured, what better way"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 27750,
    "dDurationMs": 3660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to learn about these changes\nthan by asking actual students?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 31410,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "My name is Greg; I'm from Anthropic,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 32970,
    "dDurationMs": 2007,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and today I'm joined by\nfour university students"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 34977,
    "dDurationMs": 1953,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who are here to give us the inside scoop."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 36930,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, why don't you all\nintroduce yourselves?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 38580,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Hey, my name is Zain."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 39870,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm a final year student at\nthe London School of Economics,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 42510,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I study accounting and finance."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 44580,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Hi, my name is Chloe."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 46200,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm a junior at Princeton,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 47640,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "studying psychology and computer science."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 49860,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Hi, I'm Marcus."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 51090,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm a senior at UC Berkeley,\nstudying econ and data science."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 54240,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I'm Tino."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 55073,
    "dDurationMs": 1657,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm a second-year grad student"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 56730,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at the Thunderbird School\nof Global Management"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 58860,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at Arizona State University,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 60720,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'm studying a master's\nin digital transformation."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 63690,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Amazing. Thank you for being here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 65010,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Thank you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 65843,
    "dDurationMs": 2317,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- So, let's start by setting the scene."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 68160,
    "dDurationMs": 4380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What are the vibes like on\ncampus these days with AI?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 72540,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "How are people thinking about it?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 74190,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so I did a survey not too long ago"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 76530,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on how students are using AI,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 78630,
    "dDurationMs": 3930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I saw that, you know,\n90% of students are using AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 82560,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in their day-to-day workflows,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 84150,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "using it to summarize lectures,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 86160,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "using it to answer problem sets,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 87870,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to help give feedback on assignments"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 90210,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that they had written."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 91500,
    "dDurationMs": 3412,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so, really a diverse\nsort of, like, use case"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 94912,
    "dDurationMs": 2918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for AI within students."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 97830,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's having an impact."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 99060,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Universities are having to manage that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 100650,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We're seeing changes in\nrules and regulations."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 102720,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We're seeing, you know,\nsome courses ban it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 104850,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "other courses encourage it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 106200,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so, students are in a\nbit of a gray-zone right now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 109470,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where they may not know how to use AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 112110,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I also concur."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 113460,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There is a lot of chaos\nin understanding AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 117060,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and what role it'll play in universities,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 120780,
    "dDurationMs": 987,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but at the same time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 121767,
    "dDurationMs": 1413,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there's a lot of energy surrounding it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 123180,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "especially being at Berkeley"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 124590,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and being so close to\nAI hype in the Bay Area."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 127860,
    "dDurationMs": 4980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I also agree that, like, over\n90%, if not basically everyone"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 132840,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "uses AI in some way or form,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 136050,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "mostly in the form of chatbots,\nyeah, like, summarizing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 140730,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "lectures, doing assignments,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 142950,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "answering questions where\nor when teachers, TAs,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 147990,
    "dDurationMs": 1898,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, can't answer them for you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 149888,
    "dDurationMs": 1954,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I will say there is\nalso a lot of confusion"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 151842,
    "dDurationMs": 2388,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on, like, administrations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 154230,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or, like, a professor's end\non how AI can play a role"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 159330,
    "dDurationMs": 3231,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the classroom, and we're\nslowly seeing some changes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 162561,
    "dDurationMs": 1389,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "around that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 163950,
    "dDurationMs": 4230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- As business students, I see\neven myself and my colleagues,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 168180,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, we use AI for a\nlot of different things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 170910,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We use AI to understand"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 172110,
    "dDurationMs": 4302,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and analyze business\ncases, do market research,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 176412,
    "dDurationMs": 3648,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just come up with financial\nresearch, as well,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 180060,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so people use that for that as well."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 182850,
    "dDurationMs": 3690,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "People also use AI, as\nwell, to complete quizzes,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 186540,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, like, when you don't have time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 188010,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause when you're a grad\nstudent, sometimes you've got"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 190170,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "multiple jobs that you're working,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 191940,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you don't always have time."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 193800,
    "dDurationMs": 1882,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, sometimes, you can see someone"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 195682,
    "dDurationMs": 3218,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who just, you know, quickly\nsubmit answers and everything."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 198900,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, that's the bad side of it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 200430,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that, when you're in grad\nschool, you know it's supposed"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 203490,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be, like, a time for you to expand"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 206130,
    "dDurationMs": 2723,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "your critical thinking, a\ntime for you to be someone"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 208853,
    "dDurationMs": 2707,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who is, like, more decisive,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 211560,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "someone who has, like, substance\nin how you make decisions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 214710,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so, that's, I think,\nthe bad side of it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 217530,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I would say definitely the vibes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 219180,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are, like, really chaotic right now."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 221130,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Both I guess in a good and bad way."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 223260,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think the good,\nobviously, like, Zain said,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 224880,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there's a lot of exploration\nand cool projects"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 227340,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and stuff popping up."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 228660,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The bad is because everything\nis such a gray area."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 231600,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It can be very difficult to stay resilient"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 234180,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and hold yourself accountable."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 235650,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's very easy to just be\nlike, \"I'm just gonna give up"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 237902,
    "dDurationMs": 3268,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and feed this all to AI and\nnot do any of the thinking."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 241170,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I've noticed that there's\na lot of tension, as well,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 243690,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "between, I guess, like, the line"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 244950,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of how much is over-relying on AI,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 246810,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or how much is it good"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 248250,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to actually have, like,\nan actual cooperation"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 250680,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "between those two."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 251970,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I have also noticed that\nsome people are really into it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 255240,
    "dDurationMs": 900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so they use it a lot"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 256140,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in terms of, like, all of\ntheir different workflows,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 258510,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "while others, like my humanities"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 260070,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and maybe some social science friends"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 261480,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are a bit more hesitant and\nhave a bit more concern."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 264630,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, there seems to be"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 265830,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a growing, like, identity,\npolarization effect"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 268530,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I think will be really\ninteresting to see how it goes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 271350,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I'm curious, you say\nthat they're hesitant."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 274110,
    "dDurationMs": 4290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Are they hesitant but still\nusing it pretty regularly,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 278400,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or is it a mix of some are using it a lot,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 280740,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "some are not using it at all?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 281573,
    "dDurationMs": 877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, great question."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 282450,
    "dDurationMs": 1732,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think there's a spectrum."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 284182,
    "dDurationMs": 2438,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "A lot of, especially, like,\nthe pure humanity students"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 286620,
    "dDurationMs": 1453,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "have just completely opted out,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 288073,
    "dDurationMs": 2987,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think, because, often, in\ntheir classes and research,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 291060,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there's a lot more of just close reading,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 293700,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "while other, I think,\nlike, for social science,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 295650,
    "dDurationMs": 3030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I have noticed a slow trend\nwhere they're trying it out more"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 298680,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just seeing AI being applied"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 300480,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "beyond just, like, pure computational"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 302670,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or, like, machine learning, like, context,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 304740,
    "dDurationMs": 1080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which has been cool."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 305820,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And a lot of computer science"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 308280,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and also, like, other engineering classes,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 310140,
    "dDurationMs": 3810,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's still kind of a taboo to use AI."
    } ]
  }, {
