    "dDurationMs": 980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah. Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 638100,
    "dDurationMs": 4740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I've seen in the past few hackathons"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 642840,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or entrepreneurship classes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 644040,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where a lot of students have been looking"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 646980,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "into, like, healthcare use cases,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 648540,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "mixing computer vision with a Claude API"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 652320,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to interpret a person's, like, emotions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 657960,
    "dDurationMs": 3430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for, like, a mental health\nuse-case, like, signs of stroke"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 662400,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "via, like, a camera on,\nlike, someone's phone"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 664560,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or, like, a separate,\nlike, medical device."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 667800,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or even signs of, like,\ndementia for example."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 670710,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And all of them has\nbeen really interesting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 674190,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- It's so cool that people\nare spending their time"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 675990,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "doing that in school, 'cause\nthat is kind of the magic"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 677820,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of being a student is you do\nhave time to just work on ideas"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 680580,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and try new things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 681600,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and come up with projects\nthat are just for fun."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 683910,
    "dDurationMs": 840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They're just the side projects."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 684750,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, absolutely."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 685583,
    "dDurationMs": 1267,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah. Cool."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 686850,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, let's talk about learning with AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 689940,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think one of the more\ntricky parts of this"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 693270,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that, you know, AI can be a tool"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 695190,
    "dDurationMs": 2168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to help you learn about\nanything you wanna learn,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 697358,
    "dDurationMs": 2542,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but it can also be used as a crutch"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 699900,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to maybe prevent learning\nif you lean on it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 701970,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, I'm curious how you\neach personally balance that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 705450,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how you see students balancing it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 707520,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and if you see students at your university"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 709020,
    "dDurationMs": 990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "balancing it well."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 710010,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think initially what we noticed"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 713790,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was that even, like,\namongst our classmates,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 716400,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at first it was just like,\nwhatever the AI gives you,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 719190,
    "dDurationMs": 870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's what you put."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 720060,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then, it's, over time,\nattitudes have started to change."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 723510,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We're like, \"Let's just\nput a little more effort,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 725490,
    "dDurationMs": 1810,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and not even just, \"let's just put effort"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 727300,
    "dDurationMs": 1820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in what we're putting together.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 729120,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Because let's say you have a group project"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 730950,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they're, like, four or five people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 732570,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on that group project;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 733530,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "everyone gets a different part."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 735270,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And if everyone just does the first thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 737160,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that AI gives them,\nthat's not gonna produce"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 739110,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a very good project at all."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 740700,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think one thing about AI and education"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 742860,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that it's very telling\nof students' motivations,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 746220,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, why you're at university."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 747870,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think students, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 749010,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can typically group three\nobjectives for university."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 753330,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The first I would say is to learn,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 755400,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to, you know, to deepen your understanding"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 757080,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in your chosen topic."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 758850,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I would say a second objective"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 760260,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is to, you know, position\nyourself for a career,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 763440,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, get a good job."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 764550,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think the third is the\nsocial element of university"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 766980,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where students are coming to network,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 769110,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to have fun, enjoy themselves."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 770970,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think, like, those are\nthe three broad objectives"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 773070,
    "dDurationMs": 3540,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for students, and every student\nweights those differently."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 776610,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, some students prefer, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 778110,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they're coming to learn,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 779280,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they don't really care\nabout the social aspect of uni,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 781890,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and there are other students\nwho, you know, they're coming"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 784110,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because they want to get a good job,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 785460,
    "dDurationMs": 1197,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they want to enjoy university,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 786657,
    "dDurationMs": 2537,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they don't really care\nabout the learning really."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 789194,
    "dDurationMs": 2736,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think AI and especially\nhow students use AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 791930,
    "dDurationMs": 2230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is very telling of those motivations."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 794160,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, there are some\nstudents who are using it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 796320,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to complete work for them;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 797550,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, to do it on their behalf."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 799200,
    "dDurationMs": 2277,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And those are typically the\nstudents who want to save time"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 801477,
    "dDurationMs": 1833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and want to, you know, put their efforts"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 803310,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and motivations towards\nother things, which is fine."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 806370,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there are some students\nwho, you know, are staying away"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 808410,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from AI, or using it proactively."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 810750,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They're using it in ways that\nreinforce their learning,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 812970,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that make them better\nand make them stronger."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 814680,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And those are typically\nstudents that, they want"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 816750,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to learn themselves, they want"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 817800,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to, you know, have some\ndepth to their knowledge."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 820380,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so, I think that's\nwhat AI is revealing,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 821940,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, why you're really at university,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 823440,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because we have the\ntools now, to be honest,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 825360,
    "dDurationMs": 3146,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to get through university\nwithout actually learning much."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 828506,
    "dDurationMs": 2284,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's our responsibility now as students"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 830790,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to, you know, use this\ntool to, you know, achieve"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 834240,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "your own individual outcomes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 835530,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If you want to learn, you can."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 837030,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And if you want to bypass,\nyou know, a lot of the exams"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 839610,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and assignments, you\ncan pretty much do that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 842040,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I don't think there's gonna\nbe any sort of, like, rules"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 844860,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or regulations that come\nin place that can change"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 847200,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how students use AI,\nbecause, like, fundamentally,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 850350,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I don't see how that would be possible."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 852180,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so, I think the responsibility"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 853590,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is in the student's hands;\nit's like, you're in control."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 857190,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, definitely."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 858023,
    "dDurationMs": 2797,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I actually agree, and I\nthink a lot of, for how I use"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 860820,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and approach AI is, like, intention."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 862500,
    "dDurationMs": 2083,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think, even before I\nactually start prompting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 864583,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or asking it to do stuff,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 866460,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I like to think about am I asking it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 867900,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to, for example, directly\ncomplete a task for me?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 870480,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or is it more of, like,\nsomething that I'm brainstorming"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 872550,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'd like to think about it\nfrom different perspectives?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 874890,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think that piece\nis, like, I'm starting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 877470,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to see a lot more happen,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 878730,
    "dDurationMs": 3570,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause I think AI is very\ngood as, like, a catalyst"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 882300,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for especially implementing\nand building things."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 884490,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But the intention, I think, really comes"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 886020,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from the students themselves."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 887310,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I really resonate with that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 888570,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think, when these AI\nchatbots start coming out"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 891810,
    "dDurationMs": 4590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a few years ago, either because\nof the technical limitations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 896400,
    "dDurationMs": 4020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "back then, or just of\nhow little we understood"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 900420,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about AI at the time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 902430,
    "dDurationMs": 3049,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the typical workflow was\njust you ask the chatbot"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 905479,
    "dDurationMs": 1181,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a question, you get an answer,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 906660,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you do that maybe,\nlike, 50 to a hundred times"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 910440,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "across different conversations."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 912030,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Now I think people are becoming smarter"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 914760,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, like you said, are becoming more"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 916050,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "intentional with how they're using it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 917910,
    "dDurationMs": 2533,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We're starting to have, like,\nmore extended conversations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 920443,
    "dDurationMs": 4067,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "across talking about one specific topic."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 924510,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I've started, like, when I'm studying,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 926880,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'll have projects on Claude\nwhere I would have one"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 932070,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for each class; upload, like, the syllabus"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 934380,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and a bunch of different\ncourse content I'd take in"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 936360,
    "dDurationMs": 4830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for each project, and have a\nbunch of conversations acting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 941190,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as, like, individual files in,\nlike, a folder for example."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 944100,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And with these chatbots being\nable to, in recent years,"
