  }, {
    "tStartMs": 967320,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Right now, with one example,\nis that in, like, CS classes,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 973117,
    "dDurationMs": 2813,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I know a few professors who do say,"
