  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1313910,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But when I asked them that question,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1315860,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a lot of them just\ndefaulted to, \"Oh, Claude"
