  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1355730,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, I feel like, if institutions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1357710,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or schools can't really\nadapt to this quick enough,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1360170,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there is a danger in\nit just kind of skewing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1362180,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and going into a more polarized direction."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1364670,
    "dDurationMs": 2982,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I will say, though, the sentiment"
