  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1402680,
    "dDurationMs": 4410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on the side or things they\nwant to make or explore."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1407090,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think a lot of\nstudents just kind of need"
