  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1411080,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and what's out there."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1412400,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And back to the point about cheating,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1413840,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think a lot of students\nare also realizing that AI"
