  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1439265,
    "dDurationMs": 1095,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay. Yeah.\n- Yeah, I agree."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1440360,
    "dDurationMs": 2936,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think students are\nevolving, you know, with AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1443296,
    "dDurationMs": 2824,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think, when it first came\nout, everyone's very excited."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1446120,
    "dDurationMs": 3030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Students, you know, were\nusing the outputs directly,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1449150,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but now, like Marcus\nsaid, you know, people,"
