  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1468260,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, I know, you know, how it responds,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1470660,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'm learning more about the tool,"
