  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1473030,
    "dDurationMs": 2697,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and as a result, my interactions\nwith it are getting better."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1475727,
    "dDurationMs": 2114,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And like you said, we're students."
