  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1523940,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to speak for you or to give your ideas."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1526370,
    "dDurationMs": 4164,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, in that way, I feel that\nthere's that, like, first level"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1530534,
    "dDurationMs": 3126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of, like, using it like\nyou mentioned, like, maybe."
