  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1533660,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But then, you get to a level"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1535160,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you need to, in our case, explain"
