  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1539120,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what do you mean and everything."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1541010,
    "dDurationMs": 4257,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, it's not so much a case of\nlike, yes there's that level"
