  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1546920,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, doing just, like, small quizzes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1548870,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But then, in our instance\nas well, you actually have"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1551390,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to always defend your position,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1553010,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so you have to know what\nyou're talking about."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1555140,
    "dDurationMs": 4350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Let's talk about, after\ncollege, entering the job market."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1559490,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "First of all, maybe we\ncan do, like, a thumbs up,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1562370,
    "dDurationMs": 930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "down, middle."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1563300,
    "dDurationMs": 3753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "How does everyone feel about\ngetting a job after graduation?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1569360,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Like, constantly just like this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1570770,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay. Okay. Okay."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1573650,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Tell me more."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1575480,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay, well, I guess, like, the good ones"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1577910,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think is, like, just having AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1580070,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be, like, a better, like, companion"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1582140,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for, like, practicing for\ninterviews, brainstorming,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1584690,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "tailoring the resumes, et cetera."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1587060,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Unfortunately, the downside\nis that also companies"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1590150,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are obviously using AI a lot more,"
