  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1613550,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but it's just, like, kind of\na question on a screen for me,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1615950,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then I'm just,\nlike, talking to myself."
