  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1641120,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I agree with you,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1642440,
    "dDurationMs": 2506,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "especially, like, the\nscreening job candidates."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1644946,
    "dDurationMs": 3044,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's so painful because you can realize,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1647990,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, from the entire, \"Hi,\nI would like to invite you"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1650690,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to apply for this job,\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1651980,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "right up until you submit your CV."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1654290,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You've put time together,\ntailored your application,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1656630,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "everything, and then 15 minutes\nlater, \"Sorry, we regret"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1659570,
    "dDurationMs": 1137,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to inform you.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1661970,
    "dDurationMs": 1992,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when did you have time,\nyou know, to review."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1663962,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, exactly,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1664795,
    "dDurationMs": 2365,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the AI-generated email.\n- The AI-generated email."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1667160,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, that's, like, I think the\nreally, like, big downside"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1670280,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1671113,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The upsides really are that\nAI fluency has become a major"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1676430,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, for example, consulting firms now,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1678500,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I know the top four consulting firms,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1680990,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they used to hire generalist MBAs,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1683360,
    "dDurationMs": 3630,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but now they're looking for\nMBAs who've got AI fluency."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1686990,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, if you understand,\nlike, how do you apply AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1689810,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to different industries,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1691100,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then you're, like, their\nnumber one candidate."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1692810,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Actually, back to, like, Chloe's point,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1694730,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I have had an AI, like,\ninterview me before."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1697250,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Really?\n- Wow."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1698083,
    "dDurationMs": 1477,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And it was so nice."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1699560,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It would give me responses\nlike, \"Your response"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1702710,
    "dDurationMs": 4380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was super invigorating and\ninformative and exciting.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1707090,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then, \"Let's move on\nto the next question.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1708830,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Did you get the job?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1709790,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- No, but it was because I didn't qualify."
