  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1715760,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think they were looking\nfor, like, rising juniors,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1717950,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I was a rising senior."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1719900,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, I still got auto screened."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1722900,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But it wasn't as bad\nas I thought, I guess."
