  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1733670,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I actually kind of enjoyed\nhaving a nice interviewer"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1737270,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as an AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1739154,
    "dDurationMs": 1026,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I agree. I agree."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1740180,
    "dDurationMs": 4890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Okay, speaking of, you\nknow, interesting uses"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1745070,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of AI, Merriam Webster named\n\"slop\" the word of the year,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1750230,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so I'm curious what AI\nslop means to you all,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1752780,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and how do you see it impacting the people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1755510,
    "dDurationMs": 1203,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "around you on campus?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1757610,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think, like, AI slop for me"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1759590,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is when I receive an output from Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1762200,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or any other AI tool"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1763880,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I know that if I had\njust used my own brain,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1766130,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, I could have come up with\nsomething better than that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1768110,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, that's kind of slop for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1770270,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, I think, just going\nback to job applications,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1772370,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when I'm asking it to,\nyou know, help me write"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1773810,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a cover letter, for example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1774830,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is a major use case\nfor a lot of students,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1777590,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it gives me a cover\nletter which is so generic;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1779840,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, every other student\nis applying with this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1782180,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it's like, \"This is\nnot gonna get me the job.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1783920,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, that's, you know, the AI slop."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1785450,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think it's really funny\nthat, like, AI responses"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1788120,
    "dDurationMs": 3539,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "can be so generic that it's\nits own voice at this point."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1791659,
    "dDurationMs": 2871,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's, like, a common,\nlike, meme, I guess, for AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1794530,
    "dDurationMs": 3460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to have a lot of M-dashes\nand certain sound bites."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1797990,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, you're absolutely right,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1799700,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or like, \"Let me think about that.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1802370,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or it has this, like,\ntwo-sentence structure"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1804470,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that it keeps giving me"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1805303,
    "dDurationMs": 2557,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whenever I try to write, like, letters"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1807860,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or scripts, for example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1810020,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it's like, \"You're\nnot reinventing the wheel."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1812210,
    "dDurationMs": 1900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, you're building the next Tesla.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1814945,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1815778,
    "dDurationMs": 1412,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1817190,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Honestly, it's everything\nyou guys have said."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1819260,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah, and then, like,\nyou get the feedback,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1822860,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you get the output, and\nthen it's up to you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1825410,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, some people, if you\nwork with them in a group,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1828410,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sadly they'll just paste that,"
