  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1830210,
    "dDurationMs": 1987,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you could see that at the end,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1832197,
    "dDurationMs": 2483,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"Would you like Claude to keep\" you know."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1834680,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Oh."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1835513,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, that's-"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1836563,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Claude can make mistakes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1837396,
    "dDurationMs": 914,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Retry.\n- Claude can make mistakes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1838310,
    "dDurationMs": 870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Retry."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1839180,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah, that's my definition of AI slop."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1841310,
    "dDurationMs": 1287,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- So, you mentioned group projects,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1842597,
    "dDurationMs": 1683,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think this is a big thing, right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1844280,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When you have a group of\nfour or five at university,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1847070,
    "dDurationMs": 2523,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you have maybe a\n5,000 word report due,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1850550,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how do you guys go about it?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1851750,
    "dDurationMs": 3930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Because at my university, there\nis sometimes some students"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1855680,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who, like, don't want to\nuse it, and I remember,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1858050,
    "dDurationMs": 930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, one student was saying,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1858980,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, \"I'm gonna do this project"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1860600,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "before you guys get your\ngrubby AI hands on it.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1863570,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I was like, \"Okay.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1865130,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But, like, some students really-"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1867020,
    "dDurationMs": 1093,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Did he use that term?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1868113,
    "dDurationMs": 2036,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Grubby AI hands.\n- Grubby AI hands."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1870149,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Oh, man.\n- Oh my god."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1870982,
    "dDurationMs": 1528,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Some students feel\nreally strongly against it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1872510,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and when you're working\nin a group, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1873620,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have to take into consideration\nother people's thoughts."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1876560,
    "dDurationMs": 855,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- True."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1877415,
    "dDurationMs": 2715,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, what are your\nguys' thoughts on that?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1880130,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I can go first, 'cause we do a lot"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1881870,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of those 5,000 words kind of projects,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1884570,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like maybe create a business case"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1886640,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "out of this business dilemma."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1888140,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And how we do it, like,\nhow we've recently started"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1890840,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "working on it is we'll take\nthe paper or the question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1893930,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and we'll, like, create an outline."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1895670,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We'll maybe ask AI, \"Can\nyou create an outline"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1897710,
    "dDurationMs": 870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for this paper for me?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1898580,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, \"What should be in\nthis paper\" and stuff."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1901310,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then, we divide it amongst ourselves."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1903470,
    "dDurationMs": 3630,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- One thing I like doing a lot\nis, yes, using that outline"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1907100,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and for, like, this example\nof, like, a 5,000 word report"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1910460,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "amongst, like, four people split\nit into different sections,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1912950,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then for each person\ncovering each section,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1917150,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's up to you and how you want to use AI,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1921050,
    "dDurationMs": 1743,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whether you use it or not at all."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1923687,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And what I like to do\npersonally is have a lot"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1926747,
    "dDurationMs": 1383,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of, like, bullet points"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1928130,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or just, like, thought-dumping into Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1930950,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and working with it to kind\nof structure my thoughts."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1933890,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, going from random, like, bullet points"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1936590,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or one-off phrases into\nmore of an outline,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1940590,
    "dDurationMs": 1580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then into paragraphs"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1942170,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I can kind of manually\nedit the wording of"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1944720,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so it's more like my voice and tone."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1947930,
    "dDurationMs": 3400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then, one thing I really\nlike asking Claude actually"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1952430,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is to give the context of who\nis usually reviewing my work."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1957530,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "For a job application, for example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1959120,
    "dDurationMs": 4223,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's, like, this VP or, like, recruiter,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1963343,
    "dDurationMs": 3367,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then, like, in a class\nit's like a professor or a TA,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1966710,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I ask, like, \"Hey,\nhere are some criteria."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1971630,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Rate my work score out of 10.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1974570,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I would do that maybe,\nlike, two to three times,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1977210,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it would always gimme reasons"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1978890,
    "dDurationMs": 4230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about, like, why it\ngraded, gave me a score,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1983120,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a certain score.\n- That's a good idea."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1984290,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- And what I could work and improve on."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1986930,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "A lot of times, I like the feedback."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1988190,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Sometimes I think some of the feedback"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1991160,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is a bit overzealous or ridiculous."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1994940,
    "dDurationMs": 3273,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And in newer models,\nlike Sonnet and Opus 4.5,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2000490,
    "dDurationMs": 3660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they're starting to give,\nlike, a bit of urgency"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2004150,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whenever I ask it to\nevaluate my work too much,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2006820,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "almost like they're calling\nme out for overthinking."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2010060,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "After maybe, like, the third try"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2011470,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of, like, this, like, evaluation,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2012700,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they'll be like, \"It's ready to ship.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2014020,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2015790,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Nice. Nice."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2016623,
    "dDurationMs": 3247,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Are there AI slackers in group projects?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2019870,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, people who you can tell"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2020980,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are not turning on their\nbrains for the project?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2022510,
    "dDurationMs": 2123,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- With their grubby AI hands."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2024633,
    "dDurationMs": 1177,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, definitely."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2025810,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think something that is most helpful"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2027550,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for me is, like, obviously\nbesides alignment"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2030280,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just, like, being very\nintentional when you're using AI,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2033580,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a lot of face-to-face time actually."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2035530,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, what I like to do when\nI work on a group project"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2037780,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is just block out a time\nchunk, sit down with my group,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2041170,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and we just talk about\nit as we work through it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2043660,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think, very often, it's easy"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2045010,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to feel like you're alone\nwhen you're just working"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2046900,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on a group project on your self,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2048910,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is what makes AI so tempting,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2051250,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause you're just like,\n\"Oh, what if I just had"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2052600,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "someone write it for me?\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2053620,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But if we were all forced\nto, let's say, sit down"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2055870,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and talk together, like\nif someone had a problem"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2058090,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and work through it, I think\nthat definitely helps a lot"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2060220,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with the more human piece\nof working together."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2062620,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah,\n- I agree."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2063760,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Okay, I'm gonna shift us\nto some rapid-fire questions."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2066970,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, each should be, like,\none to two sentences maximum."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2070330,
    "dDurationMs": 4365,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, my first question is,\nwhat is a tip that you have"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2074695,
    "dDurationMs": 1725,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for students right now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2076420,
    "dDurationMs": 2715,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who are navigating this whole\nworld of AI in education?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2079135,
    "dDurationMs": 1045,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Learn it. Learn it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2080180,
    "dDurationMs": 1580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Learn how to use it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2081760,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's only to your\nadvantage if you understand"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2084550,
    "dDurationMs": 2425,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how it can optimize your career,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2086975,
    "dDurationMs": 2165,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or if you decide to be an entrepreneur,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2089140,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how it can optimize your business."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2091060,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- If you're trying to learn new concepts"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2093700,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or revising for exam, start a new project"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2096970,
    "dDurationMs": 4110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for every class you're\ntaking in university."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2101080,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Try and paste in all the relevant files,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2104500,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and perhaps you already\nhave existing conversations"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2106660,
    "dDurationMs": 1907,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you've worked with Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2108567,
    "dDurationMs": 2183,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to go through certain assignments"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2111670,
    "dDurationMs": 2583,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and set the writing style to concise mode."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2115420,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's been most helpful for me"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2117010,
    "dDurationMs": 4560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to get a quick rundown\nin an efficient manner"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2121570,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of, like, every concept I\nneed to cover for an exam."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2124990,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Substack and open-source materials."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2127510,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There are so many cool\npeople out there who know"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2130000,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the best or newest ways to use\ndifferent types of AI tools,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2133240,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and what I've found most\nhelpful is just soaking"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2135130,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that up like a sponge, and then applying"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2137230,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it to my own projects."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2138730,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Nate Jones on Substack."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2140200,
    "dDurationMs": 850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "He's pretty good."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2142150,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "My tip would be use the styles."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2144400,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, you mentioned it\nbriefly, the concise mode."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2147160,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The learning mode is fantastic."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2148540,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If you want to augment your own brain"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2150610,
    "dDurationMs": 3510,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and augment your own skills,\nuse the learning mode."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2154120,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It will ask you questions back."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2155500,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Be confident in your replies back,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2157090,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you genuinely will get"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2158530,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a better output than just\nleaning on Claude by itself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2162610,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- All right. Next question."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2164350,
    "dDurationMs": 3930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "How do you, in one sentence,\npersonally draw the line?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2168280,
    "dDurationMs": 3510,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "How do you draw the line\nbetween using AI as a tool"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2171790,
    "dDurationMs": 1642,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and using AI as a crutch?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2173432,
    "dDurationMs": 2348,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Where do you find that balance?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2175780,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- If I was in a room like this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2178180,
    "dDurationMs": 3903,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I can't explain or\ndefend what I've built,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2182920,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "even if someone asks,\nlike, a super critical"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2185020,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or specific question,\nI think that's the line"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2187540,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you kind of don't really\nunderstand what's going on."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2190870,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I totally resonate with that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2191980,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's a mix of, like, the\nownership and intentionality."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2195760,
    "dDurationMs": 4620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If you can't really\nexplain what you've done"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2200380,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "along with also including what\nAI's role was in your work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2203980,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or what you're doing,\nthen that's a line for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2206230,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah. That's another\nline for me as well."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2208570,
    "dDurationMs": 3030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, I should be able to\nexplain it like I'm explaining"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2211600,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to someone in fifth grade,\nwhatever the output is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2215080,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I should be able\nto present it as well,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2217690,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "even at a graduate level,\nanything that I prepared."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2220270,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, that's my line."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2221680,
    "dDurationMs": 3540,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Anything I create with AI,\nI should be able to give"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2225220,
    "dDurationMs": 4110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that lower level and that\nupper level explanation."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2229330,
    "dDurationMs": 1558,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I agree with all of you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2230888,
    "dDurationMs": 2522,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think, if you're not\ncomfortable with the content"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2233410,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you've produced,\nat the end of the day,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2235750,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, is that really yours\nor are you just stealing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2238810,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that content from Claude?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2240610,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so, just feeling comfortable,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2243070,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "having some sort of,\nlike, feeling of ownership"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2245350,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I've produced this\nwork, that's the line for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2248530,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, there have been times"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2251110,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where I've submitted pieces\nwhich are, like, fully AI,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2253750,
    "dDurationMs": 3750,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it's just like, this is\nnot gonna take me anywhere"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2257500,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at the end of the day."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2258730,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But you learn that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2259563,
    "dDurationMs": 1057,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I think that's the\nbiggest thing with students"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2260620,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that it takes time\nto learn those feelings,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2263380,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you kind of have to give it that time."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2265600,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, a student might have\nto submit something 100% AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2268900,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to realize that, actually,\nthis was not beneficial for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2272170,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think universities need\nto be conscious of the fact"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2274810,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that students will learn,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2275920,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you've gotta trust\nthe students, right?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2277660,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "At the end of the day,\nthey live their own lives,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2281860,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, you know, you wanna set yourself up."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2283750,
    "dDurationMs": 1892,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You have that equality between students,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2285642,
    "dDurationMs": 1618,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and we'll figure it out."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2287260,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, we'll figure out what works,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2288490,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where it's good, where it's not."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2290170,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, like holding space."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2291850,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2293350,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I feel like that's a\nfantastic place to end."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2294790,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I just wanted to say,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2295810,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, that \"We'll\nfigure it out\" mentality."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2297790,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This whole time, I kind of expected"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2299440,
    "dDurationMs": 2576,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this conversation to shift into doomerism,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2302016,
    "dDurationMs": 1654,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it never quite did."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2303670,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think, like, all of you"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2305620,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are, you know, thoughtfully\npositive about the future"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2308920,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in a way that, I think, is really exciting"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2310900,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and really encouraging."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2313330,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, thank you all for being\nhere, for being honest,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2316540,
    "dDurationMs": 2545,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and yeah, I really\nappreciated this conversation."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2319085,
    "dDurationMs": 935,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Thank you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2320020,
    "dDurationMs": 1248,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Thank you for having us."
